---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTAButton from '../components/CTAButton.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About US - Assignment Help Talk"
  description="Assignment Help Talk is a professional writing platform that connects talented writers with everyone who needs assignment help writing services."
  canonical="https://assignmenthelptalk.com/about-us/"
  robots="index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-video-preview:-1, max-image-preview:large"
>
  <article class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-dark mb-6">Quality Service – Satisfied Customer</h1>

    <div class="mb-8">
      <CTAButton text="Place Your Order Now" href="/order-now/" />
    </div>

      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Assignment Help Talk is a professional writing platform that connects talented writers with everyone who needs assignment help writing services.</p>
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark mb-4">Trusted by 100,000 + happy customers</h2>
    </section>
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark mb-4">Offering Unbeatable Services</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">No matter what kind of writing you need, we'll do it quickly and accurately. Our professionalism is the best in the industry. Below are the services we offer.</p>
    </section>
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark mb-4">Writing</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Just give us the instruction and make the payment. We will write the paper from scratch.  The full payment is after you're fully satisfied</p>
    </section>
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark mb-4">Rewriting</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We will completely rewrite your paper if you've done the research, and you need a specialist to make it top notch  – originality guaranteed.</p>
    </section>
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark mb-4">Editing</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">If you have a task that needs some last minute changes, send it to us with instructions. We'll have it back to you ASAP. .</p>
    </section>
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark mb-4">Proofreading</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">For a professional proofreading, we go over your finished work, checking spelling, grammar, and formatting to make sure the assignment is top-notch</p>
    </section>
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark mb-4">Benefit from Assignment Help Talk- Extras</h2>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-3 mt-6">24/7 Support</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We're always online day and night. Connect with customer support around-the-clock for any orders or urgent questions.</p>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-3 mt-6">Unlimited Edit</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We do all revisions free of charge. Ask your writer for adjustments and you'll have them in no time!</p>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-3 mt-6">Flexible Prices</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">All the prices are negotiable. Just contact us on the chat and you will get a good discount.  Affordability is in our DNA.</p>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-3 mt-6">Quick Turn Around time</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">No matter how tight the deadline, You can get your paper done.</p>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-3 mt-6">Free Plagiarism Reports</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Originality guaranteed. We provide a FREE Plagiarism  report with every assignment because originality is one our main priority.</p>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-3 mt-6">Quality Control</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We have a quality control department. Every essay must go through an extra eye to ensure quality.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <CTAButton text="Get Expert Help Now" href="/order-now/" />
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
